Rimini Street, Inc. (Nasdaq: RMNI) is a global provider of enterprise software products and services, the leading third-party support provider for Oracle and SAP software products and a Salesforce partner. The Company offers premium, ultra-responsive and integrated application management and support services that enable enterprise software licensees to save significant costs, free up resources for innovation and achieve better business outcomes. To date, more than 4,000 Fortune 500, Fortune Global 100, midmarket, public sector and other organizations from a broad range of industries have relied on Rimini Street as their trusted application enterprise software products and services provider. 
The company is widely recognized by clients, leading industry analysts (including Gartner, Forrester, Constellation Research and Nucleus), and financial analysts as the leader in a large, fast growing market with tremendous upside and an extremely strong value proposition that resonates with CIOs and CFOs. 
We actively seek a  Product Strategy Director, Oracle resident . This role can be based anywhere in the US. 
Rimini Street views all employees as partners, and is committed to providing an exciting, participatory and team-oriented work environment. In addition to our very competitive compensation packages, be prepared for challenging professional growth and fun along the way in our work-hard, play-hard corporate environment. 
Position Summary 
The Oracle Product Strategy Director is responsible for defining Oracle product strategy, as well as defining product vision, product requirements and positioning, of the Oracle Product Line. You will be responsible for leading the ORACLE product strategy, designed to enable ORACLE licensees to respond to new opportunities and challenges accompanying today's changing IT landscapes. In addition, you will guide the strategy and product requirements of initiatives that align closely to customersâ€™ needs and objectives and then make sure they fit into Rimini Street's business model. You will collaborate closely with Sales, Product Marketing and Corporate Marketing to help them understand product positioning, benefits and target customers for Rimini Street support offerings. These executions will directly align with business and sales growth goals and objectives. 
Essential Duties and Responsibilities 
Provide assistance and guidance in the development of the product strategy and programs that drive demand for Rimini Street services and solutions 
Responsible for defining the product strategies and requirements 
Responsible for helping to define product vision and positioning and working with Oracle product marketing on executing their go to market strategies 
Provide market and product research and competitive analysis to progress the product line 
Integrates market knowledge, insights and a strong user focus to help our organization create great offerings 
Collaborate with the Oracle Product Line GM to create action plans that are do-able and will create business impact 
Partner with executives, sales, marketing and service delivery to assess and review current product strategies 
Facilitate working sessions to identify questions and hypotheses to ensure our organization delivers on our customersâ€™ needs 
Participate in thought leadership initiatives: blogging, writing papers, conference presentations 
Champion best practices and innovative thinking to continually improve the product line 
Demonstrate clear and compelling points of view, including unique approaches to solving problems with strategic insights and actionable advice
